{"id": 929, "date": "1987-01-10T11:00:45", "date_gmt": "1987-01-10T19:00:45", "guid": {"rendered": "http://estreetshuffle.com/?p=929"}, "modified": "2026-06-03T17:14:52", "modified_gmt": "2026-06-04T00:14:52", "slug": "matr-jesse-malin-and-bruce-springsteen-do-you-remember-rocknroll-radio", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/1987/01/10/matr-jesse-malin-and-bruce-springsteen-do-you-remember-rocknroll-radio/", "title": {"rendered": "Do You Remember Rock&#8217;n&#8217;Roll Radio"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p>It amazes me that Bruce has only covered this once, at Light of Day 2014&#8211;this would be an instant highlight at an E Street Band concert.</p>\n<p>For now, though, we&#8217;ll have to be content with Bruce and Jesse Malin teaming up for The Ramones&#8217; &#8220;Do You Remember Rock&#8217;n&#8217;Roll Radio?&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/fx7TEDtp5u8?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p>Here&#8217;s the original for good measure&#8211;because there&#8217;s no such thing as too much airplay for the classics.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Gi9a7IdRiBI?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p>Recorded in 1979 and released the following year, this was Joey Ramone&#8217;s paean to the classic sound of rock and roll and his lament at how modern rock had become so commercialized.</p>\n<p>Ironic (and prescient) at the time, it plays sincerely today, when rock and roll is virtually gone from all but the oldies stations.</p>\n<p><strong>Do You Remember Rock &#8216;n&#8217; Roll Radio<br />\nFirst performed:</strong> January 18, 2014 (Asbury Park, NJ)<br />\n<strong>Last performed:</strong> January 18, 2014 (Asbury Park, NJ)</p>\n<p>\u00a9 March 7, 2018 / June 3, 2026</p>\n", "protected": false}, "excerpt": {"rendered": "<p>A one-time-only cover of a Ramones classic.</p>\n", "protected": false}, "author": 1, "featured_media": 69653, "comment_status": "open", "ping_status": "open", "sticky": false, "template": "", "format": "standard", "meta": {"_monsterinsights_skip_tracking": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_active": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_note": "", "_monsterinsights_sitenote_category": 0, "_jetpack_newsletter_access": "", "_jetpack_dont_email_post_to_subs": false, "_jetpack_newsletter_tier_id": 0, "_jetpack_memberships_contains_paywalled_content": false, "_jetpack_memberships_contains_paid_content": false, "footnotes": "", "jetpack_publicize_message": "", "jetpack_publicize_feature_enabled": true, "jetpack_social_post_already_shared": true, "jetpack_social_options": {"image_generator_settings": {"template": "highway", "default_image_id": 0, "font": "", "enabled": false}, "version": 2}, "jetpack_post_was_ever_published": false}, "categories": [3617, 5], "tags": [461, 63, 55, 460], "class_list": ["post-929", "post", "type-post", "status-publish", "format-standard", "has-post-thumbnail", "hentry", "category-it-takes-two", "category-meeting-across-the-river", "tag-do-you-remember-rocknroll-radio", "tag-jesse-malin", "ta